# Deploying to App Store

This plan outlines the steps to build and upload the application to the App Store.

## Proposed Changes

### Versioning
- Verify current version in `pubspec.yaml`.
- Increment version number if necessary (user input might be needed).

### Build Release
- Clean the build environment: `flutter clean`.
- Build the iOS archive: `flutter build ipa`.

### Distribution
- Open the resulting `.xcarchive` in Xcode.
- Validate and Distribute App to App Store Connect.

## Verification Plan

### Manual Verification
- Verify the IPA build succeeds.
- Verify the upload to App Store Connect completes successfully via Xcode.
